From Rei Hamakawa Subject Xavier AV Extension to InterViews Dear Folks It's a pleasure to be able to announce the release of a new freeware program Xavier an audio and video extension to Xavier eXtension AV class for IntERviews is a C class library that adds multimedia capability to It allows composite multimedia objects to be built from media Specifically it adds audio and video objects to the classes available in InterViews and it does so without changing the source code for the original classes though several configuration files for InterViews need to be changed via a patch file Currently the Xavier audio classes are only supported on SUN workstations with an audio interface such as the Xavier has been tested in the following environments SUN Machine SPARCstation IPC OS SUN or later C SUN C NEC EWS Machine OS EWS UX V C C It can be obtained via anonymous ftp from in pub contrib and We are preparing a mailing list for information regarding If you are interested please contact I will add your e mail address to our Reference o Rei Hamakawa Hizekazu Sakagami Jun Rekimoto Audio and Video Extension to Graphical Interface Toolkits The Third International Workshop on Network and Operating System Support for Digital Audio and Video San Diego Rei Hamakawa e mail o o C C Systems Research Laboratories o NEC Corporation O Miyazaki Chome TEL O Miyamae ku Kawasaki FAX O Kanagawa JAPAN